          "message": { "text": "An attacker who gains access to the inter-agent message bus may spoof supervisor delegation messages, causing specialist agents to act on forged orchestration commands.", "markdown": "Authenticate all inter-agent messages with HMAC signatures using per-session keys. Implement message source validation before specialist agents process delegation commands." },
